title: AD: Subaru pre-owned deals – available from RM76k!
text:
Home » Special Coverage » Advertorial » AD: Subaru pre-owned deals – available from RM76k! AD: Subaru pre-owned deals – available from RM76k! 24 February 2017 12:29 pm / Comments are Disabled 
Motor Image is now having fantastic deals on management and test drive Subaru vehicles, available for a limited time only. The pre-owned units now start from as low as RM76k, so if you’re looking for a new ride, this is the time to pounce! 
The special limited management and test drive units are all well-maintained, very good condition vehicles. They are now available at irresistibly attractive prices and are a not-to-be-missed opportunity. 
Head on over to selected Motor Image Subaru showrooms for more details. You can also contact Eddie ( 012-5050901 ) in Kuala Lumpur, Lawrence ( 012-3109966 ) in Petaling Jaya, JC ( 012-6654005 ) in Cheras, Kenny ( 016-4370077 ) in Bukit Mertajam, Nazim ( 016-7176786 ) in Georgetown or Alan ( 012-7733292 ) in Johor Bahru. Harvinder Singh Sidhu thinks there's nothing better than Formula 1, not even sliced bread. Having written about cars since 2006, he plunged head first into the industry out of a passion for all things four-wheeled and everything in between. The F1 enthusiast has been following the sport since 1999 and has been keeping up with it since. In between races he keeps himself busy as the host of the Driven motoring TV programme and as our version of the Joker.
